OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of
OL,4,Cthe old Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FSo the end looms for what was once
OL,7,FGrampian ` the wee station with the big
OL,8,Fname.
OL,10,FIt lost its name and local programmes
OL,11,F20 years ago but its news service lived
OL,12,Fon.
OL,14,FThe STV News at Six in the northern
OL,15,Fhalf of Scotland was really North
OL,16,FTonight in disguise.
OL,18,FNow it too is to go.
OL,20,FSTV is proposing to change its news
OL,21,Fservice.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
