OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of
OL,4,Cthe old Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FThere will, subject to Ofcom approval,
OL,7,Fbe one news service presented from
OL,8,FGlasgow for both central and northern
OL,9,FScotland.
OL,11,FThe financial situation facing STV is
OL,12,Fserious. It lost #200,000 in the first
OL,13,Fhalf of the year. Advertising is down
OL,14,F#5m.
OL,16,FBut there is profound concern amongst
OL,17,Fpoliticians in the north of Scotland.
OL,19,FOf course the question now is whether
OL,20,FOfcom will allow this change.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
