OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of
OL,4,Cthe old Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FOr might some compromise emerge? Or
OL,7,Feven outright rejection?
OL,9,FOfcom is not the poodle some accuse it
OL,10,Fof being.
OL,12,FIn 2013 it helped reinstate a fuller
OL,13,Fnews service for the ITV Border region.
OL,15,FBut since then the marketplace has
OL,16,Fchanged.
OL,18,FAdvertising is down. Linear TV is not
OL,19,Fdead but some clearly prefer on demand.
OL,20,FYounger people are not consuming old
OL,21,Fmedia.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
