OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of
OL,4,Cthe old Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt is all a very hard circle to square.
OL,8,FMeantime caught in the middle are 30
OL,9,FSTV journalists set to lose their jobs.
OL,11,FIf the change happens, "Grampian" will
OL,12,Fbe the first of the official C3
OL,13,Ffranchise areas of old to completely
OL,14,Fdisappear.
OL,16,FIt will be fascinating to see if this
OL,17,Fproposal actually goes ahead.
OL,19,FOr will Ofcom and political pressure
OL,20,Flead to the plan being scrapped?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
